        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>Even cau­tious and ex­pe­ri­enced driv­ers can run into un­ex­pected prob­lems when nav­i­gat­ing the roads.</p>
    <p>In such in­stances, a dash­board cam­era can be use­ful to have as it cap­tures con­tin­u­ous footage of incidents hap­pen­ing at the front and rear of your ve­hi­cle.</p>
    <p>Some give users a cloud stor­age op­tion to save the footage. This elim­i­nates the worry of not hav­ing enough stor­age space on their mem­ory cards.</p>


